{"tid":2030100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★深圳婦空置單位28年　上門收樓驚見陌生人住緊","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T05:10:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e4515b644bb38e8a3713e1f477db4bcb80ef7c58","tid":2030100,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"事源是深圳的一位張女士，稱自己在1992年曾花33.2萬元（人民幣，下同，約36.2萬港元），買了深圳寶安華天花園一套144平米（約1550呎）的單位，多年來未有裝修便空置，亦未辦理房產證，單位現已升值至600萬元（約654萬港元），近日張女士想起這個單位，便找親戚幫忙上門看看，不料卻發現單位竟已經裝修好並有人居住。<br />\n<br />\n單位現住戶聲稱，由2001年起入住單位，涉事單位是父親從他人手上購買，但也一直沒有辦理房產證，目前未能聯繫上賣家，父親亦受此事「生氣」到要入院。而管理屋苑的職員指，只知道涉事住戶一直有繳交水電費、物業費；有居民則表示，現有住戶並不是業主，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>是撬鎖自行搬入去的。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2648137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2648137&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=d33265c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2648137</a>"},{"pid":"71dca5323ac6b8c01a81020f5a4b358125e44371","tid":2030100,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783760df27b0d9a8db8ba0c156ceabf29bc0210d","tid":2030100,"uid":224657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"這就是中國.jpg"},{"pid":"7f9c49dee75f5cd44a603470069cf93860c2992a","tid":2030100,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"呢d都叫新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces